name: EABluetoothAccessoryPickerError.Code
desc: The error codes that may be passed in an error object for the Bluetooth picker completion block.

items.name: case alreadyConnected
items.desc: The specified accessory was already connected.

items.name: case resultNotFound
items.desc: The specified accessory could not be found, perhaps because it was turned off prior to connection.

items.name: case resultCancelled
items.desc: The user canceled the picker alert.

items.name: case resultFailed
items.desc: Selecting an accessory failed for an unknown reason.
